    Class Description
    CauseDB
    CauseDB.java is the Data Access class used to retrieve a single cause or a List of all causes from the database.

    DamageDB.java is the Data Access class used to retrieve a single damage or a List of all damages from the database.
    DBUtil
    This class will create the Entity Manager Factory object, based on the Work Order Persistence Unit.

    NotificationDB.java is the Data Access class used to retrieve, create, modify and delete Notification objects.

    TechnicalObjectDB
